Exit Program
Use Switch statement to call the corresponding function 
Give the option to save the edited image to a file 
Repeat until user decides to exit the program


Load Function 
Open File for the reading 
Read the height & width
Close File

Display Function
Loop through the 2D array for the image
Print characters corresponding to brightness levels


Edit Function
Add the ability to dim & brighten image 

Save Function
Open file for writing 
Write height & width
Close file

Crop Function
Prompt user to edit the length and width of image
Save the new data and return it 

